### PHASE 6: Frontend — Logging UI (The Core)

**Goal:** Users can actually complete their habits from the habits page.

| Build | Details |
|---|---|
| `useHabitLogs` hook | `logHabit`, `updateLog`, `deleteLog` mutations + today's logs query |
| `habitLogService` | API calls for log CRUD |
| Update `HabitCard` | `boolean` → checkbox. `numeric` → number input with progress. `timer` → start/stop/reset stopwatch. `checklist` → checkable sub-items |
| `TimerWidget` component | Stopwatch with start/pause/reset, returns seconds on save |
| `ChecklistLog` component | Renders checklist items with checkboxes for today |
| `NumericLog` component | Number input + "out of {target} {unit}" label |
| Update `HabitsPage` | Fetch today's logs, pass to `HabitGrid` → `HabitCard` |
| Optimistic updates | Checkbox/input updates immediately, reverts on API error |

**Files to create/modify:**
- `src/services/user/habitLogService.ts` (new)
